=== Safespot ===
It is possible to safespot Brutus with ranged, magic or a 2 tile reach melee weapon in the southernmost part of the pen. This method requires you to lure Brutus to the north side of the two Food troughs. Stepping in between them (out of reach for Brutus) makes him unable to use his charge attack, nor can he path towards you in any way. This allows you to safely kill him without having to worry about special attacks.

